name: Damn tourist stealing my children!
description:
In this little game, you have to rescue your ducklings from the evil tourists that want to kidnap them!  (because they think your babies are so cute) Move with WASD to pick up your babies; you can also quack with SPACE to scare off the tourists that kidnapped a duckling !

Art, Level Design, additional coding : ElTacos

AI Coding : Walfos
